name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Table of Contents Generator for Medium

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a table of contents to your medium blog post

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Want to easily create a table of contents for your medium blog post? This extension will do that for you! Simply install, write "toc" wherever you want to create the table of contents, click Generate and the extension will do the rest.
